{"tid":401437,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大男更衣室偷拍男生沐浴　內地研究助理認罪候判","createTime":"2017-09-15T15:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T20:44:56.000Z","uid":78546,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"646375c5c0af476e0ee5b38fac030150d7dcefa1","tid":401437,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:07:38.000Z","msg":"來自內地的研究助理，在中大男更衣室內偷拍男子沐浴，被事主當場搶奪手機，更揭發他另有偷拍另一男子。助理今在沙田法院，承認兩項不誠實使用電腦罪，他求情時指，青年時發現自己的性取向，惟內地思想較保守，他會就此尋求協助，而他原想往外地升讀博士的計劃亦擔心受影響。裁判官把案押後至明年1月13日判刑，以候被告的感化及社會服務令報告。<br />\n<br />\n被告林珅，25歲，承認今年10月30日，在中大男更衣室偷拍兩名男子。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，男事主案發當日中午在中大一男更衣室洗澡時，發現有人從門隙用手機偷拍，即伸手奪去手機，保安制服亦即把被告逮著並報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方到場後，在手機內發現兩段事主，及兩段涉另一名男子的沐澡片段，該些片段均在同一天在同一更衣室內拍攝。<br />\n被告求情稱不敢向家人透露自己性取向<br />\n<br />\n辯方律師求情時指，被告在中文大學社工學系取得碩士，並因成績優異而獲聘為研究助理，他原打算到外國升讀博士，但擔心因本案可能影響簽證申請。<br />\n<br />\n律師指被告已辭去研究助理的工作，又提到被告中學時已發現自己的性取向，但因在內地的家人偏向保守，被告不敢向他人透露，現時已向性治療師尋求協助。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：STCC4481/2016"},{"pid":"0d8cf0afb91e3809fd35373f99b98352e08bf5a3","tid":401437,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:07:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/61831?utm_content=bufferac263&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F61831%3Futm_content%3Dbufferac263%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=be7GtzZNjLjSt6Uiz7uTDHadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=8833d98c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/61831?utm_content=bufferac263&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a>"},{"pid":"a802240708bb631a2c7523a28e7ffa5bdd805eef","tid":401437,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef6bc3f962181e7c220c9050d35bb9de6df60f0","tid":401437,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3cfefe1547fadc721cbbdfc3f9a8f0fb3ac774","tid":401437,"uid":138762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:50:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">This</span></span>"},{"pid":"7a5a5422427e7d259f61c76ec51bfda02d7e2111","tid":401437,"uid":37005,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"被偷拍嗰兩個一定好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad3dc8555fa381ad0bdc1b709879766cb257203","tid":401437,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"社工愛抽插"},{"pid":"7ac8595a287c30a3863d94ead0cf2cba5de98ecf","tid":401437,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T16:29:55.000Z","msg":"內佢老母地"},{"pid":"9a696de414a8746a31e3efa2adf74aa71889d3e8","tid":401437,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T18:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被偷拍嗰兩個一定好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88b06fd1d30600fca9c84d8a5535a763442f6d6","tid":401437,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T20:44:56.000Z","msg":"返支那讀博士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}